Module net.etf.project
Package net.etf.project.statistics

Class SummaryReport

java.lang.Object
net.etf.project.statistics.SummaryReport
public class SummaryReport extends Object
The SummaryReport class is responsible for generating and printing a summary report of the rental receipts. It calculates various financial metrics such as total income, discounts, promotions, and costs related to the maintenance and repair of vehicles.
